@startuml
title KiTicket — implemented component view
left to right direction

actor Customer
actor Organizer
actor Administrator
component "React / Vite client" as Web
component "NestJS API\ncontrollers, guards and services" as API
database "PostgreSQL\ndurable application state" as DB
collections "Redis\nseat locks and queue sequence" as Redis
queue "RabbitMQ\ndomain-event queue" as MQ
component "Socket.IO gateway" as WS

Customer --> Web
Organizer --> Web
Administrator --> Web
Web --> API : REST /api
Web --> WS : authenticated Socket.IO
API --> DB : TypeORM
API --> Redis : Lua lock scripts, INCR
API --> MQ : publish and consume\nnotification events
API --> WS : user/event updates

note bottom of API
One deployable modular monolith.
RabbitMQ delivery is not backed by an outbox/inbox.
end note
@enduml

